SUMMARY:Winter 2026 Dance Performance
DESCRIPTION:Wilmette Center for the Arts Dance Alliance & Elevé \nWinter 2026 Dance Performance\nSupport the Wilmette Center for the Arts dance students! Attend a special Winter season dance performance with our talented Dance Alliance and Elevé dance troupes. \nMonday\, March 23 at 4:30 pm \nFREE Performance (no ticket required) \nPerformances take place at the Community Recreation Center Auditorium\, 3000 Glenview Rd. \n\n  \n  Download PDF\n      \n          \n          \n           Save This Page as a PDF
