SUMMARY:26-27 Before & After School Programs Posted
DESCRIPTION:Register Soon for 26-27 Before & After School Programs!\n\nMarch 31 – Programs post online for browsing\nApril 14 – Priority* registration opens\nApril 21 – Resident** registration opens\n\n*Priority registration applies only to families currently enrolled in 25-26 BSR and/or ASR\, and extends to siblings entering BSR and/or ASR. \n**Resident registration applies to all D39 & D37 students (or incoming students) not currently enrolled in BSR and/or ASR programs. \n  \nGet to know our Before & After School Programs below… \nBefore & After School Programs (Grades K-6) include:\n\nBefore School Rec | Before School Rec runs 7-8:30 am and is held at:\n\nHarper Elementary – Open to students attending Harper\nMcKenzie Elementary – Open to students attending McKenzie and Central\nRomona Elementary – Open to students attending Highcrest and Romona\n\n\nAfter School Rec | After School Rec runs 3:15-6 pm and is held at:\n\nCommunity Recreation Center – Open to students attending all D39 schools and Avoca\nCentral Elementary – Open to students attending Central\nMcKenzie Elementary – Open to students attending McKenzie\nRomona Elementary – Open to students attending Romona\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  Download PDF\n      \n          \n          \n           Save This Page as a PDF
URL:https://wilmettepark.org/event-list/before-after-school-programs-posted/
LOCATION:Online\, United States
CATEGORIES:Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://d11ixze0kvt635.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/26141231/ASR2526-LIVE-Fi.jpg
END:VEVENT
