SUMMARY:WCT Spring Production Ticket Sales
DESCRIPTION:Ticket Sales begin March 31 for…\nWilmette Children’s Theater spring production: Beetlejuice Jr. \nPerformances: \n\nFridays\, April 17 & 24: 7 pm\nSaturdays\, April 18 & 25: 2 pm\nSundays\, April 19 & 26: 2 pm\n\nSupport the arts and enjoy a show hosted by the talented students of the Wilmette Children’s Theater! Limited seating available. All seats reserved. \n\nTICKETS $13\nGeneral sales open: March 31 at 10 am\n\nPurchase tickets online\, or at the Community Recreation Center front desk. For more information\, please call 847-256-9686. \n\n  \n  Download PDF\n      \n          \n          \n           Save This Page as a PDF
URL:https://wilmettepark.org/event-list/wct-spring-production-ticket-sales/
LOCATION:Community Recreation Center
CATEGORIES:Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://d11ixze0kvt635.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/18122429/BTJ26-TICKETS-Fi.jpg
